
We are now at the menu area.

To select the buttons you wish to use, you can talk or touch the displays.

The normal menu button is a representation of a standard menu that lists all of our available meals.

You may see our vegetarian recommendation at the special button.

You can play tic tac toe with your opponent, who is pepper, during our other gaming session.

You can touch my head to proceed to game session, touch my left hand to proceed to special menu,

or touch my right hand to proceed to the normal menu!

Play with it all you want!